-- EUROPE RESEARCH ROUNDUP-Hannover Re, Lundin Petroleum, Securitas 
-- 
-- Thu Aug 07, 2014 02:16AM EDT
-- None



Aug 7 (Reuters) - Securities analysts revised their ratings and price targets on several European companies, including Hannover Re and Lundin Petroleum, on Thursday.

HIGHLIGHTS * Hannover Re <HNRGn.DE>: DZ Bank raises to buy from hold * Lundin Petroleum <LUPE.ST>: UBS raises to buy from neutral * Securitas AB <SECUb.ST>: UBS cuts to sell from neutralFollowing is a summary of research actions on European companies reported by Reuters on Thursday. Stock entries are in alphabetical order.   * Ageas SA <AGES.BR>: SocGen cuts target price to 39 euros from 40.3 euros; rating buy * Amara Mining <AMARA.L>: BMO ups to outperform (speculative)  * Amara Mining <AMARA.L>: BMO raises target price to 30p from 25p * Banco Popular <POP.MC>: UBS cuts target to 4.60 euros from 6.10 euros; rating neutral * Carphone Warehouse <CPW.L>: Barclays reinstates with overweight; price target 420p * Credit Agricole <CAGR.PA>: UBS raises target to 13.3 euros from 12.6 euros; rating buy * DNO <DNO.OL>: UBS starts with neutral; target price of Nok 20.50 * DO Deutsche Office AG <PMOX.DE>: Berenberg starts with buy; price target 3.85 euros * Ferrexpo Plc <FXPO.L>: Citigroup cuts target price to 170p from 190p; rating buy * Hannover Re <HNRGn.DE>: DZ Bank raises to buy from hold * ING <ING.AS>: UBS raises target price to 12.50 euros from 12.40 euos; rating buy * International Personal Finance <IPF.L>: Berenberg cuts target to 525p from 565p; hold * Kuka <KU2G.DE>: Morgan Stanley raises target 47 euros from 42 euros; rating equal-weight * Lundin Petroleum <LUPE.ST>: UBS raises to buy from neutral * Phoenix Mecano AG <PM.S>: UBS cuts target price to Sfr 520 from Sfr 550; rating neutral * Securitas AB <SECUb.ST>: UBS cuts to sell from neutral * Standard Chartered <STAN.L>: UBS raises target price to 1315p from 1300p; rating buy * Swiss Re <SRENH.VX>: JP Morgan cuts target price to Sfr 77 from Sfr 79; rating underweight * UCB <UCB.BR>: Jefferies raises target price to 45 euros from 40 euros; rating underperform * Victrex Plc <VCTX.L>: Berenberg starts with buy; price target 1950p * Vivendi SA <VIV.PA>: Barclays raises target to 20.50 euros from 19.75 euros; equal weight